An Act Changing the Name of the San Pedro Elementary School in Barangay San Pedro, Municipality of San Jose, Province of Antique, to Assemblyman Segundo Moscoso Memorial School
Section 1. The name of the San Pedro Elementary School in Barangay San Pedro, Municipality of San Jose, province of Antique, is changed to Assemblyman Segundo Moscoso Memorial School.1avvphi1
